# <type>(<scope>): <subject>            ≤100 chars · imperative · lowercase start · no period
#   type: feat|fix|docs|style|refactor|perf|test|build|ci|chore|revert
#   scope: web|api|governance|data|security|web3|deps|scripts|adr|i18n|…
#
# --- body (what & why; wrap ~100 cols) ---------------------------------------
#
#
# Change:        <what changed>
# Security:      <impact or "none">
# Quality/Tests: <test status / validation run>
# Architecture:  <impact or "none">
#
# --- footers (git trailers) --------------------------------------------------
# Refs: TASK-XXX-NNN
# ADR: ADR-NNN
# BREAKING CHANGE: <if any>
# Co-authored-by: Name <email>
#
# Standard: docs/governance/commit-and-pr-conventions.md
# Enable once:  git config commit.template .gitmessage
